description: Table: Prescheduling - Stores pre-scheduled data for radio access network resources, including time, location, cell ID, and associated identifiers.  Columns: dateTime (timestamp of prescheduling), Area_Name (geographic area), CellId (unique cell identifier), Id2 (alternative cell identifier), Id3 (auxiliary identifier), Id4 (auxiliary identifier), vsDataType (data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion (version of data format), Prescheduling.preschedulingId (unique prescheduling identifier).
